name: Strings and Spheres
description:
Vibrations Series Finale.

A small glimpse at the multiple travels I've had. 
I'm fortunate to have had a partner in all of them.
A witness to infinity and a mirror into my voyage.

Edited in after effects using spherical video edited in Insta360 Studio.
